			A list of Fighter emotes
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
farena    - You invite another to the arena.
fbleed    - You don't have time to bleed!
fcard     - places an ace of spades on a corpse. (corpse required)
fcot      - you request a player to meet you at COT.
fdance    - you challenge someone to fight or "dance".
fdazzle   - you display your fine mastery of your weapon.
feye      - you eyeball someone.
fflex     - a fighter's way of flexing.
fgrin     - a fighter's way of grinning.
fgrunt    - you grunt.
fring     - challenge someone to step in the ring.
fhbutt    - you butt heads. Gets better with higher strength.
fhug      - a big bear hug.
fpoint    - to point at someone saying: "this is the one."
fpoke     - a bone crushing poke.
fshake    - a painful hand shake.
fsmooth   - Damn you're smooth...
fthink    - you think very carefully.
fwipe     - you wipe the blood off on a corpse. (corpse required)

Syntax is: <emote> or <emote> <target>
